<h1>{{ title }}</h1>

<p>Themes give your project a cohesive look and feel across the entire Web Awesome library.</p>

<p>A theme sets typography, spacing, borders, shadows, and how <a href="/docs/tokens/color#variant-colors">variants</a>
  show up on components — all as <a href="/docs/tokens">design tokens</a>. Two themes can share a <a
    href="/docs/color-palettes">color palette</a> and <a href="/docs/tokens/color#variant-colors">variant colors</a> and
  still feel completely different. Each pre-built theme ships with a default palette and may include custom overrides
  for individual components.</p>

